name: indexed-context
description: >
  Always-on agent intelligence layer powered by OpenWolf. Provides file index
  awareness, learning memory, token tracking, bug history, Design QC, Reframe
  framework selection, and daemon/cron management. Activates at session start to
  give coding agents project context before any action. Works across all
  rd3-supported platforms.
version: 1.0.0
emoji: 🛠️
